(in a security setting where decisions must be explained.) Tj
/F2 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 72.0 640.0 Tm
(Deep Learning: Medical Image Analysis) Tj
/F1 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 72.0 610.0 Tm
(A well-established application is the automated screening of retinal photographs to detect) Tj
/F1 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 72.0 586.0 Tm
(diabetic retinopathy, a leading cause of blindness. A trained system grades the severity of disease) Tj
/F1 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 72.0 562.0 Tm
(in each image so that patients who need a specialist are prioritized quickly \(Gulshan et al., 2016\).) Tj
/F1 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 72.0 532.0 Tm
(Deep learning fits this problem well. The input is raw pixels that contain complex spatial) Tj
/F1 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 72.0 508.0 Tm
(patterns, such as tiny hemorrhages, lesions, and subtle changes in texture spread across the whole) Tj
/F1 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 72.0 484.0 Tm
(image. No person can write down a short list of features that captures all of this reliably. A) Tj
/F1 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 72.0 460.0 Tm
(convolutional neural network learns a hierarchy of features directly from labeled images, moving) Tj
/F1 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 72.0 436.0 Tm
(from simple edges to lesion shapes, and it can reach expert-level accuracy when trained on) Tj
/F1 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 72.0 412.0 Tm
(enough data \(Gulshan et al., 2016\).) Tj
/F1 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 72.0 382.0 Tm
(Simple machine learning is not suitable here. A traditional algorithm cannot consume millions of) Tj
/F1 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 72.0 358.0 Tm
(raw pixels directly; it depends on features that an engineer defines ahead of time. Hand-crafting) Tj
/F1 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 72.0 334.0 Tm
(features that describe every relevant lesion is impractical, and it would miss patterns that humans) Tj
/F1 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 72.0 310.0 Tm
(do not think to look for. Accuracy would fall well short of what a clinical screening tool requires.) Tj
/F2 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 72.0 254.0 Tm
(Conclusion) Tj
/F1 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 72.0 224.0 Tm
(The right choice is driven by the structure of the data and the supply of labeled examples. When) Tj
/F1 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 72.0 200.0 Tm
(the important features are few, already known, and worth keeping visible, simple machine) Tj
/F1 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 72.0 176.0 Tm
(learning is faster, cheaper, and easier to trust. When the data is high-dimensional and the patterns) Tj
/F1 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 72.0 152.0 Tm
(are too complex to describe by hand, deep learning earns its added cost. Matching the method to) Tj
/F1 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 72.0 128.0 Tm
(the problem, rather than defaulting to the most powerful tool available, is what makes a solution) Tj
/F1 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 72.0 104.0 Tm
(effective.) Tj
